title: Ep. 459 - Psycho Monday
description:
Cyber Monday turns into Psycho Monday, from the TV ads selling cheap consumer goods to the politicians trying to sell themselves. We will examine all the sociopathy. Then, speaking of psychos, the Deep State goes on offense before the Inspector General releases his report on the origins of the Russia investigation. Can we the people beat the bureaucrats? Date: 12-03-2019
